last_episode_to_air.name: The One Time We're All Together
last_episode_to_air.overview: The couples go for a weekend to Ibiza, where Esther and Luis get a little stingy. Everyone watches Pedro's new — and weirdly familiar — series.

name: Alpha Males
overview: Pedro, Luis, Raúl and Santi are four friends who feel a little lost in the new world of empowered women, each trying to adapt in their own haphazard way.

episodes.name: Deconstructing
episodes.overview: Pedro loses his job. Santi's daughter moves in with him. Luis's wife is unhappy about their sex life. Raúl's plan to propose doesn't go as he imagined.

episodes.name: Life's What Absorbs You
episodes.overview: Pedro's bad at being unemployed. Luis and Esther try talking to a sex therapist. Raúl learns something new about his parents, and Santi about Álex.

episodes.name: Toxic Masculinity
episodes.overview: Raúl moves in with Santi who's having mixed success on his dates. Daniela's career is going well, much to Pedro's chagrin. Esther tries some medication.

episodes.name: Ibizan Herbs
episodes.overview: The lads go to Ibiza. Santi tries to make them think about their language. Pedro might have a problem. Well, two actually. Esther goes to the gym. A lot.

episodes.name: Sensitive Heteroflexibles
episodes.overview: Raúl tries to adjust to his new situation. Pedro tries to sign up for unemployment, and makes a big mistake. Luis and Santi look for a gay friend.

episodes.name: Look What You've Done
episodes.overview: The lads attend a seminar on toxic masculinity. Santi has a successful date. Raúl keeps striking out. Daniela offers Pedro a job. Luis makes a discovery.

episodes.name: When Was The Last Time You Cried?
episodes.overview: Luz proposes something new. Pedro and Daniela aren't loving their work arrangement. Luis and Esther try to negotiate. Santi wants to commit, or does he?

episodes.name: Just When We Were Doing So Well
episodes.overview: Pedro becomes a different type of influencer. Raúl and Daniela think Luz and Pedro might be up to something. Santi can't make up his mind.

episodes.name: The Moses Of Sexist Pigs
episodes.overview: Pedro's "pro-masculinity" videos go viral, jeopardizing Daniela's career. Eugenia springs an unwelcome surprise on Santi. Luz and Raúl take a big step.

episodes.name: Either The Course Is a Failure, Or We Are
episodes.overview: Raúl makes a huge mistake, and Daniela makes a dramatic decision. Santi surprises Álex, but not in a good way. Luis and Esther throw a birthday party.

episodes.name: I Feel Kind of Deconstructed
episodes.overview: Pedro returns to the job market. Luis' son is being bullied at school. Raúl plans to make up with Luz, whereas Santi isn't happy with Blanca.

episodes.name: You Have Dreams?
episodes.overview: Luis' new patrol partner makes Esther jealous — and catches Raúl's eye. Pedro hires a guest to join him on a business event. Santi has a job interview.

episodes.name: The Other Way Around
episodes.overview: Santi is forbidden from flirting at work, but the temptation arises. Things heat up between Pedro and his boss. Luz has doubts about motherhood.

episodes.name: Ask Before You Enter
episodes.overview: The group travels to Málaga seeking advice from Patrick, but they end up partying at a Russian magnate's house. Esther's drama classes get out of hand.

episodes.name: Don't Go Falling in Love
episodes.overview: Raúl makes new friends. Luis suspects his wife wants more action in bed. Pedro celebrates a win at work, while Santi gets into trouble with his boss.

episodes.name: On a Monday?
episodes.overview: Raúl, kicked out of Pedro's house, matches with Santi's wife. Luz struggles with Héctor and his son. Luis explores his open relationship.

episodes.name: The Brotherhood
episodes.overview: Paula gives Santi an ultimatum. Pedro visits the urologist. Raúl pushes the friends into an experience that turns out to be too... buddy-buddy.

episodes.name: I'm Straight
episodes.overview: Esther believes Luis is gay. Santi looks desperately for the video of Paula. Pedro tries to improve his sperm quality. Raúl keeps experimenting.

episodes.name: What Does It Mean to Be a Woman?
episodes.overview: Daniela organizes a surprise party for Pedro... and invites Ángela. Esther and Luis visit a swingers club. Patricia shares shocking news.

episodes.name: The One Time We're All Together
episodes.overview: The couples go for a weekend to Ibiza, where Esther and Luis get a little stingy. Everyone watches Pedro's new — and weirdly familiar — series.
